message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously crafted to meet your needs. I believe it would be a valuable addition to your collection, and I understand its worth to you is $120. Considering its quality and the value it brings, I propose to sell it to you for $140. This price allows me to cover my costs and ensure sustainable business operations, while still providing you with a great deal. I look forward to your positive response.
